snippet.title: Algo Bot - Puzzle Programming Game Trailer (english)
snippet.description:
GET THE GAME ON STEAM
http://store.steampowered.com/app/286300/Algo_Bot/

Deep inside the Europa, a pan-galactic colonisation ship, a recycling mission goes horribly wrong. Use your algorithm special skills to command AlgoBot, a service droid and help PAL a cantankerous line manager to contain the crisis.

http://www.twitter.com/algobot
http://www.facebook.com/algobot
http://www.algo-bot.com
